---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import StudyNotesGenerator from '../../components/StudyNotesGenerator';
import SimilarTools from '../../components/SimilarTools';
---

<Layout title="AI Study Notes Generator - AI-Free-Forever">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-purple-100/50 py-16 mb-12 rounded-2xl text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        AI Study Notes Generator
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Transform complex topics into clear, organized study notes. Generate comprehensive summaries and key points for better learning.
      </p>
    </div>
    <StudyNotesGenerator client:load />
    
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-16">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Create Perfect Study Notes in Seconds</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">Struggling to organize lecture material or textbook content? Our AI Study Notes Generator transforms complex topics into clear, structured notes that make studying more effective and efficientâ€”all with just a few clicks.</p>
        
        <p class="text-lg mb-8">Powered by advanced GPT-4o technology, the AI Study Notes Generator creates comprehensive, well-organized study materials tailored to your specific subject and learning level. Best of all, it's completely freeâ€”no subscriptions, no word limits, and no hidden fees.</p>
        
        <p class="text-lg mb-8">Whether you're preparing for exams, condensing lecture material, or trying to master difficult concepts, our tool helps you create the perfect study notes to boost your learning and retention.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">How to Create Effective Study Notes Using the AI Study Notes Generator</h2>
        <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-4 mb-8">
          <li class="text-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold">Enter Your Topic</span>
            <p>Provide the specific subject or concept you want to study. The more focused your topic, the more detailed your notes will be.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="text-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold">Select Your Academic Level</span>
            <p>Choose from high school, undergraduate, or graduate level to ensure your notes match your educational needs.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="text-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold">Choose Your Preferred Format</span>
            <p>Select from outline format, Cornell notes, flashcard style, mind map structure, or detailed explanations based on your learning style.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="text-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold">Generate and Customize</span>
            <p>Click "Generate" to receive comprehensive study notes instantly. Review, edit, and personalize them to enhance your learning experience.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Why Quality Study Notes Are Essential for Academic Success</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Improve Information Retention</h3>
            <p>Well-organized notes help your brain process and store information more effectively, leading to better recall during exams.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Save Valuable Study Time</h3>
            <p>Instead of rewriting or reorganizing messy notes, start with a clear structure that maximizes your study efficiency.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Clarify Complex Concepts</h3>
            <p>Our AI breaks down difficult ideas into digestible, easy-to-understand components with clear explanations.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Identify Key Information</h3>
            <p>The AI Study Notes Generator highlights the most important concepts, definitions, and relationships, helping you focus on what matters most.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Who Should Use the AI Study Notes Generator?</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-8">
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">High School Students:</span> Simplify complex subjects and prepare effectively for exams.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">College Students:</span> Transform lengthy lectures and textbook chapters into concise, organized notes.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">Graduate Students:</span> Synthesize research papers and advanced concepts into structured study materials.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">Adult Learners:</span> Create efficient study guides for professional certifications or continuing education.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">Teachers and Professors:</span> Generate clear lesson summaries and study guides for students.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Tips for Getting the Best Results with the AI Study Notes Generator</h2>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
          <table class="min-w-full bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
            <thead class="bg-gray-50">
              <tr>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-900 font-semibold">Best Practice</th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-900 font-semibold">Why It Matters</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Be specific with your topic</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Narrower topics yield more detailed, focused notes. For example, "Photosynthesis process in C4 plants" will generate better notes than just "Biology."</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Choose the right format</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Different subjects and learning styles benefit from different note formats. Math might work better with step-by-step explanations, while history might benefit from chronological outlines.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Add your own insights</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Personalize the generated notes with your own examples, questions, or connections to enhance understanding and retention.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Use color coding or highlighting</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">After generating notes, consider adding visual elements to further organize information and improve memory recall.</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Is the AI Study Notes Generator completely free?</h3>
            <p>Yes! You can generate unlimited study notes with no word limits, subscription fees, or hidden costs.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">How accurate is the information in the generated notes?</h3>
            <p>The AI Study Notes Generator creates high-quality notes based on established knowledge. However, we recommend verifying critical information with your course materials or trusted sources.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I generate notes for any subject?</h3>
            <p>Yes! The tool supports a wide range of subjects including sciences, humanities, mathematics, business, engineering, medicine, and more.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What note formats are available?</h3>
            <p>You can choose from outline format, Cornell notes, flashcard style, mind map structure, or detailed explanations based on your learning preferences.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
