                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Limited by subscription</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">AI Model</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">GPT-4o (Latest)</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Varies, often older models</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Note Format Options</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Multiple formats available</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Limited options</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Registration Required</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">No</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Yes, with payment info</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Subject Coverage</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Comprehensive</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Often limited by specialty</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        
        <p class="text-lg mb-8">Effective studying starts with well-organized notes. With the AI Study Notes Generator, you can instantly transform complex topics into clear, structured study materials that enhance your learning, improve retention, and boost your academic performanceâ€”all completely free.</p>
        
